<p>Short-term effects of alcohol abuse can be just as dangerous as long-term effects. </p>

<p>For instance, drinking can impact your reaction time, causing you to have slow reflexes and coordination.</p>

<p>That’s why drinking and driving is extremely dangerous. Getting behind the wheel of a car can alter your perception of speed and distance, putting yourself and others at risk.</p>

